    "body" : "<p>If you want a function to do this</p>\n\n<pre><code>Object array = new String[10];\nint size = Array.getlength(array);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>This can be useful if you don't know what type of array you have e.g. int[], byte[] or Object[].</p>\n"
